data.description: Welcome to 7112 Mamie Blvd, a spacious 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home featuring over 2200 sq feet of living space. The home is filled with natural light and features upgraded fixtures, neutral paint, and tons of storage. Featuring granite counters, stainless steel appliances, the kitchen opens into the large family room, great for entertaining! A separate dining room and half bath are also on the first floor. The second floor features three secondary bedrooms, a hall bathroom. The spacious primary suite boasts two walk-in closets, tray ceilings, and en-suite bathroom with tiled shower and dual vanities. The home's exterior features a two-car garage, patio accessible via the family room, and large fenced backyard.
